data.title: About Bill Hewat
data.meta_description: Hewat Project Management is en experienced Building project Management company. We specialise in saving you time and money when building or renovating in the South Island of New Zealand. Our expertise covers a wide range of projects including commercial, residential and self build projects of all sizes.
